"title": "6669: grace, and salvation",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6669",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Deliverance through Jesus Christ is the result of accepting God's undeserved favour.</p>\n<h2>Salvation is all God's doing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:6-Rom5:8\">ROM 5:6–5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:14-Rom9:16\">ROM 9:14–9:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:7\">EPH 1:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:15-1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:15–1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19\">EXO 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:12\">ACT 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:24\">ACT 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:15-Rom5:17\">ROM 5:15–5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:2\">2CO 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:13-Col1:14\">COL 1:13–1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:16\">2TH 2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11\">TIT 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:23-Heb7:25\">HEB 7:23–7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:10\">REV 7:10</a></p>\n<h2>There is nothing human beings can do to save themselves</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:7\">TIT 3:4–3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:5-Rom11:6\">ROM 11:5–11:6</a></p>\n<h2>Salvation is not by keeping God's law</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:4\">GAL 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:20-Rom5:21\">ROM 5:20–5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:14\">ROM 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:1-Rom8:4\">ROM 8:1–8:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:21\">GAL 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:17-Gal3:18\">GAL 3:17–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:9\">1TI 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>Salvation must be accepted as a free gift by faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:9\">EPH 2:4–2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:7-Acts15:11\">ACT 15:7–15:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:30-Acts16:31\">ACT 16:30–16:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:21-Rom3:24\">ROM 3:21–3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:14-Rom4:16\">ROM 4:14–4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1-Rom5:2\">ROM 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:16\">HEB 4:16</a></p>",
